      <h1 class="h1">About Us</h1>
      <h2 class="h2 tagline">With Guzo, traveling by bus in Ethiopia is no longer about long queues, uncertainty, or guesswork. It’s about clarity, choice, and confidence — the way modern mobility should be.</h2>
      <p class="paragraph">
        Guzo is Ethiopia’s next-generation online bus booking platform, built in 2025 to transform the way people travel across the country. Designed with simplicity, convenience, and accessibility in mind, Guzo connects millions of passengers with bus operators, making travel planning faster, safer, and more reliable.
        <br><br>
        With Guzo, travelers get the widest choice of routes and buses, real-time tracking, and transparent pricing — all in one place. By digitizing and modernizing Ethiopia’s long-distance bus travel, Guzo is reducing the hassle of ticketing and helping both passengers and operators thrive in the digital era.
        <br><br>
        While proudly built for Ethiopia, Guzo has a global vision. We aim to become a regional leader in East Africa’s travel-tech space by promoting sustainable and affordable mobility solutions, inspired by the success of international bus booking platforms.
